channel.name: Ask us anything: Pitt CSC Hackathon Travel Fund

messages.content: Ask us anything about the application process here. Please limit all questions to this thread 🙂
Is a hackathon this weekend too early to apply for this?
yeah on the form it says please allow for four weeks

Is there a reason why it’s 4 weeks? idk for other people but I usually decide if I am going to a hackathon 2-1.3 weeks before the actual hackathon weekend and planning 4 weeks out seems a bit long since some hackathons don’t release their application decisions / registration until 2 weeks out or less
The tldr is that there are just a ton of hoops to go through reimburse students for a hackathon to get this initiative to work… we are small team and need time to do things
Is the hackathon fund limited to americans?
